sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Gateway
    participant StrategyService as algoshare-strategy
    participant DB as Strategy DB (Mongo/Postgres)
    participant Redis

    User->>Gateway: POST /strategies { "condition": "RSI < 30", "symbol": "BTC" }
    Gateway->>StrategyService: Forward Request
    StrategyService->>StrategyService: Validate Logic
    StrategyService->>DB: Save Strategy (Status: DRAFT)
    StrategyService-->>User: 201 Created (ID: strat_001)

    User->>Gateway: POST /strategies/strat_001/activate
    Gateway->>StrategyService: Forward Request
    StrategyService->>DB: Update Status -> ACTIVE
    StrategyService->>Redis: ADD to "Active_Strategies_List"
    StrategyService-->>User: 200 OK "Strategy Running"